  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Zombieville USA 3D</strong> is a light-hearted action romp, combining classic arcade action with modern visuals and a dash of roguelite fun.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1801520/extras/2fd5052c9381eef682c6d7be11531382.poster.avif?t=1741373611\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1801520/extras/2fd5052c9381eef682c6d7be11531382.webm?t=1741373611\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1801520/extras/2fd5052c9381eef682c6d7be11531382.mp4?t=1741373611\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play solo or with friends as you scavenge for weapons, unlock skills, and see how long you can survive before you become a midnight snack for the living dead!  Whether you played the original Zombieville USA over 15 years ago, or this is your first foray into the zombie-filled suburbs, we hope you’ll enjoy your stay!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1801520/extras/69425becfd2022eebca939cb1c12a22e.poster.avif?t=1741373611\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1801520/extras/69425becfd2022eebca939cb1c12a22e.webm?t=1741373611\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1801520/extras/69425becfd2022eebca939cb1c12a22e.mp4?t=1741373611\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > An arsenal of 39 weapons to unlock, from machine guns and shotguns, to chainsaws, rockets, energy weapons, flamethrowers, and katanas.  You name it, we probably got it. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 28 unlockable \"perks\" to level up, customizing your playstyle.  Specialize in melee weapons, explosives, whatever floats your boat. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Randomly generated weapons with unique traits keep every run unpredictable</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Infinitely scaling difficulty - go for your high score before the living dead overwhelm you!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Spectacular stylized 3D visuals.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Play solo or with online co-op for 3 players.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Designed to play great with a gamepad, but feels right at home with mouse and keyboard as well.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Zombieville USA 3D</strong> is a light-hearted action romp, combining classic arcade action with modern visuals and a dash of roguelite fun.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1801520/extras/2fd5052c9381eef682c6d7be11531382.poster.avif?t=1741373611\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1801520/extras/2fd5052c9381eef682c6d7be11531382.webm?t=1741373611\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1801520/extras/2fd5052c9381eef682c6d7be11531382.mp4?t=1741373611\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play solo or with friends as you scavenge for weapons, unlock skills, and see how long you can survive before you become a midnight snack for the living dead!  Whether you played the original Zombieville USA over 15 years ago, or this is your first foray into the zombie-filled suburbs, we hope you’ll enjoy your stay!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1801520/extras/69425becfd2022eebca939cb1c12a22e.poster.avif?t=1741373611\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1801520/extras/69425becfd2022eebca939cb1c12a22e.webm?t=1741373611\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1801520/extras/69425becfd2022eebca939cb1c12a22e.mp4?t=1741373611\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > An arsenal of 39 weapons to unlock, from machine guns and shotguns, to chainsaws, rockets, energy weapons, flamethrowers, and katanas.  You name it, we probably got it. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 28 unlockable \"perks\" to level up, customizing your playstyle.  Specialize in melee weapons, explosives, whatever floats your boat. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Randomly generated weapons with unique traits keep every run unpredictable</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Infinitely scaling difficulty - go for your high score before the living dead overwhelm you!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Spectacular stylized 3D visuals.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Play solo or with online co-op for 3 players.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Designed to play great with a gamepad, but feels right at home with mouse and keyboard as well.</p></li></ul>",
